&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>One of the reasons why working in Jupyter is so great, at least for prototyping, is because we can view our work immediately:&lt;/p>
